      "explanation": "Chinese has several words for approximation:左右，大约，差不多. 左右 comes AFTER a number/time: 三点左右 (around 3 o'clock), 十个左右 (about ten). 大约 and 差不多 come BEFORE: 大约三点, 差不多三点. 大约 is more formal; 差不多 also means 'almost the same'. You can combine: 大约三点左右 (though slightly redundant, it's used in speech).",
